cs.CC, cs.GT, cs.DS, cs.AI, cs.DM 

This paper deals with computational complexity and game theory, which are both covered by the cs.CC (Computational Complexity) and cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) sub-categories. The paper also involves algorithms and data structures (cs.DS), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and discrete mathematics (cs.DM) in its analysis and proofs.
